---
import Container from "./Container.astro"
---
<div class="services-page py-20 bg-gray-50" style="margin-top: 40px;">
    <Container>
        <h2 class="title text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-900">I nostri servizi e offerte</h2>


        <!-- Griglia di card -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-2 xl:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
            <!-- Servizio 1 -->
            <div class="service-card group relative bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md overflow-hidden">
                <div class="service-body py-12 px-8 text-center">
                    <div class="icon-container mb-6 flex justify-center">
                        <img src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/5532/5532931.png"
                             class="icon w-24 h-24 mb-4"
                             width="512" height="512"
                             alt="Preventivi gratuiti"
                        />
                    </div>
                    <h5 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Preventivi gratuiti</h5>
                    <p class="mt-4 text-xl text-gray-900 opacity-80">Richiedi un preventivo gratuito per le tue tapparelle: ti risponderemo in tempi brevi.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Servizio 2 -->
            <div class="service-card group relative bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md overflow-hidden">
                <div class="service-body py-12 px-8 text-center">
                    <div class="icon-container mb-6 flex justify-center">
                        <img src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/5285/5285806.png"
                             class="icon w-24 h-24 mb-4"
                             width="512" height="512"
                             alt="Sostituzione Tapparelle"
                        />
                    </div>
                    <h5 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Sostituzione Tapparelle</h5>
                    <p class="mt-4 text-xl text-gray-900 opacity-80">Sostituiamo tapparelle obsolete con nuovi modelli, migliorando l'efficienza e la sicurezza della tua casa.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Servizio 3 -->
            <div class="service-card group relative bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md overflow-hidden">
                <div class="service-body py-12 px-8 text-center">
                    <div class="icon-container mb-6 flex justify-center">
                        <img src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/2778/2778814.png"
                             class="icon w-24 h-24 mb-4"
                             width="512" height="512"
                             alt="Installazione Automatica"
                        />
                    </div>
                    <h5 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Installazione Automatica</h5>
                    <p class="mt-4 text-xl text-gray-900 opacity-80">Offriamo l'installazione di tapparelle motorizzate per una gestione automatica e comoda delle tue finestre.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Servizio 4 -->
            <div class="service-card group relative bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md overflow-hidden">
                <div class="service-body py-12 px-8 text-center">
                    <div class="icon-container mb-6 flex justify-center">
                        <img src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/3079/3079162.png"
                             class="icon w-24 h-24 mb-4"
                             width="512" height="512"
                             alt="Manutenzione Periodica"
                        />
                    </div>
                    <h5 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Manutenzione Periodica</h5>
                    <p class="mt-4 text-xl text-gray-900 opacity-80">Interventi di manutenzione programmata per prolungare la vita delle tue tapparelle e prevenire danni futuri.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </Container>
</div>

<style>
    .title {
        font-size: 3.0rem;
        font-weight: bold;
        margin-bottom: 50px;
    }

    .service-card {
        background-color: white;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        border-radius: 1rem;
        overflow: hidden;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        text-align: center;
        transition: box-shadow 0.3s ease;
    }

    .service-body {
        padding: 3rem;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
    }

    .service-body h5 {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        margin-top: 1rem; /* Uniformare il margine tra titolo e testo */
    }

    .service-body p {
        font-size: 1.125rem;
        opacity: 0.85;
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin-top: 1rem;
    }

    .icon-container {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .icon {
        width: 6rem;
        height: 6rem;
        object-fit: contain;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .services-page {
            padding: 40px 0;
        }

        .service-card {
            padding: 1rem;
        }

        .service-body h5 {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
        }

        .service-body p {
            font-size: 1rem;
        }
    }
</style>
